author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Fishbone performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 5, 2025.

Songs:
Party At Ground Zero 00:49
Dog Eat Dog 05:49
Last Call In America 10:22
Suckered By Sabotage 14:32
Ma And Pa 19:36
Racist Piece Of Shit 36:07

Angelo Moore - Vocals, Sax, Theremin

John “JS” Williams II - Trumpet/Vocals
